OL,3,CThree men dead after fire in west
OL,4,CLondon
OL,6,FThree people have died following a
OL,7,Ffire in London, the London Fire
OL,8,FBrigade (LFB) has said.
OL,10,FThe fire service said they received
OL,11,Freports of the blaze on New Zealand
OL,12,FWay in White City, west London, at
OL,13,F6.52pm on Saturday evening.
OL,15,FThree men were rescued from a single
OL,16,Fstorey building by firefighters and
OL,17,Ftreated at the scene, close to Loftus
OL,18,FRoad, the ground of Queens Park
OL,19,FRangers Football Club, by paramedics.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
