OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782069073
OL,3,CThree men dead after fire in west
OL,4,CLondon
OL,6,FOf these, two were declared dead and
OL,7,Fanother died later in hospital after
OL,8,Fbeing taken there for further
OL,9,Ftreatment, the LFB said.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FSpeaking from the scene, LFB assistant
OL,17,Fcommissioner Pat Goulbourne said: "The
OL,18,Ffire involved a single storey
OL,19,Fpavilion, with just over half of the
OL,20,Fstructure damaged by the fire."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
