PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782069073
OL,3,CThree men dead after fire in west
OL,4,CLondon
OL,6,FHe added: "Control officers mobilised
OL,7,Fcrews from North Kensington, Acton,
OL,8,FChiswick and surrounding fire stations
OL,9,Fto the scene.
OL,11,F"Firefighters were able to bring the
OL,12,Ffire under control by 9.25pm.
OL,14,F"The cause of the fire is under
OL,15,Finvestigation by the Brigade's
OL,16,Fspecialist fire investigation officers
OL,17,Fand the Metropolitan Police Service. "
OL,19,FThe LFB said 15 fire engines and
OL,20,Faround 100 firefighters were involved
OL,21,Fin the response.
